name: Senior #13 - Donnie
description:
Donnie is a 75-year-old former governor who enjoys collecting wigs, junk food and spreading false rumours on social media. He is very confident and optimistic, but can also be extremely inappropriate and unstable.

He is addicted to himself, something which everyone pointed out when he was 12. The problem intensified 30 years later. Donnie has lost countless jobs as a result of his addiction, specifically: feng shui consultant, weed company receptionist and deodorant tester.
